♪ My people ♪

44:19.769 --> 44:21.737
♪ Hold on ♪

44:21.737 --> 44:23.439
♪ People ♪

44:24.540 --> 44:27.510
♪ People, the time has come ♪

44:27.510 --> 44:29.779
♪ In this land ♪

44:30.646 --> 44:36.052
♪ When the
lion must
lay down with the lamb ♪

44:37.186 --> 44:39.789
♪ Brothers and sisters ♪

44:39.789 --> 44:42.892
♪ Live side by side ♪

44:44.560 --> 44:46.495
♪ Hold on to love ♪

44:46.495 --> 44:49.065
♪ Let its light be your guide ♪

44:49.065 --> 44:52.902
- ♪ My people ♪
